verbose_text: Analysis of the mRNA expression levels for other lineage markers showed that Acan (cartilage) and Pparg (fat) genes were not expressed (Ct above 32), while Bglap (bone, Ct = 28) and Myog (muscle, Ct = 28.6) genes displayed low levels of expression in C3H10T1/2 cells in non confluent conditions on plastic substrate (XREF_FIG C).
